ata-flow diagrams and all logic for MES System, Support for C# applications. Wonderware System Platform project testing, maintenance and deployment. Arrangement of reservation, stage-by-stage updating of the system at the facility. Communication with technical support, installation of fixes. Participated in the development of the BI service on Vanilla JavaScript.", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Used: C#, .NET, JavaScript, Wonderware Quick Script, Adobe Illustrator.", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "2015- 2019: Control System Programmer,  (St.Petersburg, Russia)", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Main project: School of Engineering and Technology. Development of a management system.  Development of control interfaces for smart equipment, Designed UI interface for Desktop App, Designed UI interface for Mobile (Tablet), Writing utilities in C# for integrating various equipment with control systems.", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Used: JavaScript, C#, Python, Adobe Illustrator, Extron Global Configurator, iRidium Mobile.", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "EDUCATION AND COURSES", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "2010- 2014: Bachelor in Informatics - Polytechnic University (SPbPU),", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "Faculty of Technical Cybernetics, St.Petersburg, Russia", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "2019: Online courses \u00abT-SQL for beginners\u00bb from Udemy", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"style": "Normal"}}, {"type": "paragraph", "text": "2020: Online courses \u00abWeb Development for Developers\u00bb from Scrimba", "confidence": 0.9, "metadata": {"s